# Time series including quantiles
plt.figure(figsize= (30,15))
all_data.set_index("datetime").net.plot(color = "y",label = "Net Imbalance")
plt.axhline(y=0, color='g', linestyle='--',linewidth=5,label = "Zero Line")
plt.axhline(y=all_data.net.quantile(0.01), color='r', linestyle='-',linewidth=2,label="%1 Quantile")
plt.axhline(y=all_data.net.quantile(0.99), color='r', linestyle='-',linewidth=2,label="%99 Quantile")
plt.legend(prop={'size': 15})
plt.xticks(fontsize = 15)
plt.yticks(fontsize = 15)
plt.show()

 Hour Analysis¶

In [55]:
all_data['hour'] = all_data['hour'].apply(int)
hour_stats = pd.crosstab(all_data.hour,all_data.system_direction)
In [57]:
hour_stats.columns = ["Negative occurence","Neutral occurence","Positive occurence"]
In [58]:
hour_stats["Max Observed Label"] = hour_stats.idxmax(axis=1)
hour_stats["Max Observed Label"] = hour_stats["Max Observed Label"].apply(lambda row : row[:-10])
In [59]:
hour_stats["Negative Ratio"] = np.round(100*hour_stats[hour_stats.columns[0]]/hour_stats[hour_stats.columns[:3]].sum(axis=1),2)
hour_stats["Neutral Ratio"] = np.round(100*hour_stats[hour_stats.columns[1]]/hour_stats[hour_stats.columns[:3]].sum(axis=1),2)
hour_stats["Positive Ratio"] = np.round(100*hour_stats[hour_stats.columns[2]]/hour_stats[hour_stats.columns[:3]].sum(axis=1),2)
In [74]:
hour_stats[hour_stats.columns[-3:]].plot(
    kind = 'barh',
    stacked = True,
    mark_right = True,
    figsize=(10,10))

#plt.title('Hourly Distribution of Classes',fontsize=15)
plt.legend(loc="best",prop={'size': 10})
plt.yticks(size=15)
plt.xticks(size=15)
plt.xlabel("Percentage",fontsize=15)
plt.ylabel("Hour",fontsize=15)
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
